263
00:19:39,874 --> 00:19:43,332
- Converse?
- I think your word was "chat."

264
00:19:43,544 --> 00:19:45,978
Oh. Great! All right.

265
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:49,841
Good night. Good night. Good night.

266
00:19:52,253 --> 00:19:53,481
Good night.

267
00:20:03,164 --> 00:20:06,292
