272
00:20:19,780 --> 00:20:22,112
I know, Brooksie. Just be patient.

273
00:20:25,986 --> 00:20:27,613
Come on.

274
00:20:28,189 --> 00:20:29,656
Come on.

275
00:20:30,191 --> 00:20:32,819
